name: REJUVENATE: RE-MOVE

REJUVENATE

Episode 1: RE-MOVE

Lots of stories have been written. Could be sad or happy.
As year near it's closing, all the burden need to be release for better future ahead. So let's release all the things that bothers our mind

In this REJUVENATE series, hope can be encouragement to all of us in closing this challenging year.
